            <div type="note">
                <head>Bridget Richardson</head>
                <p>Sister of Margaret Ruskin, married to ???.<!-- Entry needed here. --></p>
                <p>Ruskin may have visited his Croydon relations particularly when John James was
                    away on business, and Margaret and Bridget needed one another&#x02BC;s help
                    or company. As John grew, however, Margaret confided to John James that she did
                    &#x201C;not like to be more than a day or two at a time&#x201D; in
                    Croydon &#x201C;on Johns acct,&#x201D; since &#x201C;he observes
                    so closely and left were he any time there together the ways and manners might
                    effect him&#x201D; (<hi rend="italic">Ruskin Family Letters</hi> 148).</p>
            </div>
        </body>
